  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. A mesh-independence verification activity is declared and described in prose; its outputs are discussed in the validation narrative, but no evidence artifact carries a prov:wasGeneratedBy link pointing to that activity.",
